-- Hunter Boots Sold to Searchlight Capital Partners, Times Says
-- B y   M a t t h e w   B r o w n
-- 2011-12-17T11:22:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-17/hunter-boots-sold-to-searchlight-capital-partners-times-says.html
Saerchlight Capital Partners LLC has
acquired a majority stake in Hunter Boots, The Times reported,
citing Peter Mullens, part of the group that acquired the
company in 2006.  The sale has been made to fund expansion into  Asia , the
London-based newspaper cited Mullens as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
